"title": "8106: assurance, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8106: assurance, nature of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The God-given security which believers have in the blessings of divine grace. Believers are assured of the unfailing love of God and of their relationship with him as Father, the salvation and eternal life which he offers and the sure hope of one day sharing his glory.</p>\n<h2>Assurance of a relationship with God</h2>\n<h3>Assurance of God's unfailing love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps13:5\">PSA 13:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:13\">EXO 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:1\">PSA 51:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps130:7-Ps130:8\">PSA 130:7–130:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:10\">ISA 54:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:1\">JHN 13:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:9\">1JN 4:9</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance of acceptance by God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:8\">ACT 15:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1\">ROM 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:3\">ROM 14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:7\">ROM 15:7</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance of adoption as God's children</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:1-1John3:3\">1JN 3:1–3:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:12-John1:13\">JHN 1:12–1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:14-Rom8:17\">ROM 8:14–8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:6\">GAL 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:18\">JAS 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:7\">1JN 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:1\">1JN 5:1</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance of God's presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:8\">DEU 31:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:15\">GEN 28:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh3:7\">JOS 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:10\">ISA 41:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:8\">JER 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:20\">MAT 28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:18\">JHN 14:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:10\">ACT 18:10</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance of access to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:12\">EPH 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:2\">ROM 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8\">EPH 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:16\">HEB 4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:19-Heb10:22\">HEB 10:19–10:22</a></p>\n<h2>Assurance of salvation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:2\">ISA 12:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:13\">PSA 69:13</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance of redemption</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:25\">JOB 19:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:9\">PSA 111:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:24\">ROM 3:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:14\">EPH 1:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:12\">HEB 9:12</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance of justification</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:26\">ROM 3:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:16\">ROM 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:33-Rom8:34\">ROM 8:33–8:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:11\">1CO 6:11</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance of forgiveness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:9\">1JN 1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:14\">2CH 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:5\">PSA 32:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:12\">PSA 103:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:25\">ISA 43:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:34\">JER 31:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:3\">JER 36:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:18-Mic7:19\">MIC 7:18–7:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:47\">LUK 24:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38\">ACT 2:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:19\">ACT 3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:13-Col2:14\">COL 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance of election</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:1\">ISA 43:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:4\">EPH 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:1-Isa44:2\">ISA 44:1–44:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28-Rom8:30\">ROM 8:28–8:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:29\">ROM 11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:9\">1CO 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:9\">2TI 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9-1Pet2:10\">1PE 2:9–2:10</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance of preservation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:12\">2TI 1:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">JUD 1:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:39\">JHN 6:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:38-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:38–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:14\">2CO 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:25\">HEB 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:10\">2PE 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>Assurance of eternal life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:15-John3:16\">JHN 3:15–3:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:11-1John5:13\">1JN 5:11–5:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:30\">MRK 10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:30\">LUK 18:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24\">JHN 5:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:40\">JHN 6:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:25-John11:26\">JHN 11:25–11:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:2\">JHN 17:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:2\">1JN 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:20\">1JN 5:20</a></p>\n<h2>Assurance of a future hope</h2>\n<h3>Assurance of confidence at Jesus Christ's return</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:30-Matt24:31\">MAT 24:30–24:31</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:26-Mark13:27\">MRK 13:26–13:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:27-Luke21:28\">LUK 21:27–21:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:13-1Thess4:17\">1TH 4:13–4:17</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance on the day of judgment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:8\">1CO 1:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:13\">1TH 3:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:17\">1JN 4:17</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance in the hope of resurrection</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:40\">JHN 6:40</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:42-1Cor15:44\">1CO 15:42–15:44</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:21\">PHP 3:21</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance in the hope of glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:18\">ROM 8:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:2\">ROM 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:4\">COL 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:12\">1TH 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:10\">REV 5:10</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance in the hope of an eternal inheritance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17\">ROM 8:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34\">MAT 25:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:7\">GAL 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:15\">HEB 9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:3–1:5</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance in the hope of an eternal reward</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:12\">MAT 5:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:23\">LUK 6:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:7-2Tim4:8\">2TI 4:7–4:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:12\">JAS 1:12</a></p>",
